---
layout: default
subject: "[{{idTag}}] New {{actionLabel}}"
---
<p style="font-size: 16px; color: #1f2937; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">You have a new {{actionLabel}}</p>
<p style="font-size: 14px; color: #4b5563; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 30px 0;">
	<strong>{{byIdTag}}</strong>{{#if snippet}} — {{snippet}}{{/if}}
</p>

<!-- CTA Button -->
<table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%" style="margin: 30px 0;">
	<tr>
		<td style="text-align: center;">
			<a href="{{link}}" style="display: inline-block; background-color: #e98a54; color: #ffffff; padding: 14px 36px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px;">Open</a>
		</td>
	</tr>
</table>

<p style="font-size: 12px; color: #6b7280; margin: 15px 0;">
	You are receiving this because email notifications are enabled for this event
	type. Manage your notification preferences in your account settings.
</p>
